                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Personal telegram, to be delivered at the home of Hon. John
                        Hay, 800 Sixteenth street, Washington.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-02-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 20, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reported that the custodian of the Bermudez Lake has check with which the First
                    Assistant Secretary of State was paid and a letter from him promising the United
                    States will not intervene. The custodian and the President of Venezuela,
                    therefore, feel safe. The facts are known here by the diplomatists and many
                    others.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bowen.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
